1
00:00:05,984 --> 00:00:09,760
(2005: One Week Before An Ruoxi's Death)

2
00:00:10,484 --> 00:00:11,284
Look.

3
00:00:13,244 --> 00:00:14,043
Jiasheng,

4
00:00:15,484 --> 00:00:17,043
I want to go out to clear my head.

5
00:00:20,683 --> 00:00:21,484
Clear your head?

6
00:00:22,484 --> 00:00:23,683
Where do you want to go?

7
00:00:25,284 --> 00:00:26,403
I haven't decided yet.

8
00:00:27,563 --> 00:00:29,043
I just want to go out for a walk.

9
00:00:29,284 --> 00:00:30,004
No.

10
00:00:30,363 --> 00:00:31,164
Wait for me.

11
00:00:32,160 --> 00:00:34,004
The reconciliation is
the day after tomorrow.

12
00:00:34,043 --> 00:00:35,843
You can go after that.

13
00:00:35,924 --> 00:00:36,683
I'll go with you.

14
00:00:38,683 --> 00:00:40,363
I just want to be alone.

15
00:00:43,683 --> 00:00:44,964
It's dangerous to go alone.

16
00:00:46,884 --> 00:00:48,123
So you do know

17
00:00:49,163 --> 00:00:50,683
the current situation is dangerous.

18
00:00:59,043 --> 00:00:59,844
Ruoxi,

19
00:01:01,204 --> 00:01:02,644
as long as I promised you something,

20
00:01:02,723 --> 00:01:03,884
I will definitely do it.

21
00:01:04,483 --> 00:01:05,123
But

22
00:01:05,683 --> 00:01:06,763
you have to give me time.

23
00:01:08,443 --> 00:01:09,284
Is that so?

24
00:01:10,603 --> 00:01:12,363
When Qin Wei wanted to do that business,

25
00:01:13,083 --> 00:01:14,883
