you wouldn't touch it.

26
00:01:15,404 --> 00:01:16,404
But what happened?

27
00:01:17,163 --> 00:01:18,684
Got roped into that mess anyway.

28
00:01:20,083 --> 00:01:21,404
I know you had no choice.

29
00:01:21,963 --> 00:01:23,443
Feng forced it,

30
00:01:24,004 --> 00:01:25,083
so you had no choice.

31
00:01:25,684 --> 00:01:26,363
Right?

32
00:01:30,684 --> 00:01:32,243
I'm just a little tired,

33
00:01:33,083 --> 00:01:35,083
sinking deeper
into this world of debauchery.

34
00:01:36,644 --> 00:01:38,684
Just let me go out for a few days.

35
00:01:39,284 --> 00:01:40,924
I'll adjust on my own.

36
00:01:41,243 --> 00:01:42,484
Maybe I'll feel better.

37
00:01:43,404 --> 00:01:44,284
Okay?

38
00:01:51,296 --> 00:01:54,496
=The Glory Fades=

39
00:01:54,496 --> 00:01:57,312
=Episode 5=
(The Ice Ball Game)

40
00:01:57,312 --> 00:01:59,424
(2006: Su Yunian's Second Day at Work)

41
00:02:32,284 --> 00:02:34,163
Mr. He.

42
00:02:34,643 --> 00:02:35,844
Yunyan.

43
00:02:36,244 --> 00:02:38,043
I've missed you so much!

44
00:02:38,084 --> 00:02:39,163
You've become prettier.

45
00:02:42,723 --> 00:02:44,084
Come on, girls!

46
00:02:45,043 --> 00:02:46,084
Let's begin!

47
00:02:47,964 --> 00:02:48,883
Hello, Mr. He.

48
00:02:48,883 --> 00:02:49,804
Distinguished guests,

49
00:02:49,804 --> 00:02:51,163
I'm Jing from the Ren Class

50
00:02:51,163 --> 00:02:52,004
and from Luosen City.

51
00:02:54,564 --> 00:02:55,323
Hello, Mr. He.

52
00:02:55,323 --> 00:02:56,564
Hello, distinguished guests.

53
00:02:56,564 --> 00:02:57,244
Okay.

54
00:02:57,244 --> 00:02:58,844
No more hello.

55
00:03:00,244 --> 00:03:01,043
Yunyan,

56
00:03:01,844 --> 00:03:03,124
what's going on?

57
00:03:03,443 --> 00:03:04,643
Why are they all

58
00:03:05,364 --> 00:03:06,883
newcomers of the Ren Class?

59
00:03:08,763 --> 00:03:10,244
Forget about the Tian Class.

60
00:03:10,244 --> 00:03:11,284
At least,

61
00:03:12,244 --> 00:03:14,004
you should arrange those from Yun Class.

62
00:03:17,043 --> 00:03:18,643
Mr. He,

63
00:03:19,404 --> 00:03:22,124
you're wronging Yunyan.

64
00:03:22,244 --> 00:03:23,643
These are all newcomers.

65
00:03:23,643 --> 00:03:24,883
They're very fresh.

66
00:03:24,883 --> 00:03:25,524
Get lost!

67
00:03:25,763 --> 00:03:27,364
How dare an assistant talk to me!

68
00:03:28,323 --> 00:03:29,364
Get lost!

69
00:03:31,643 --> 00:03:32,443
Don't block my view!

70
00:03:38,763 --> 00:03:39,564
Yunyan,

71
00:03:41,244 --> 00:03:43,163
