72
00:03:46,643 --> 00:03:47,844
Let me tell you.

73
00:03:48,964 --> 00:03:50,723
Stop messing around here.

74
00:03:52,043 --> 00:03:53,084
They're still fresh?

75
00:03:54,124 --> 00:03:55,244
If I wanted fresh ones,

76
00:03:55,244 --> 00:03:57,364
would I need to come here?

77
00:03:57,763 --> 00:03:58,603
Among these girls,

78
00:03:58,603 --> 00:03:59,124
tell me

79
00:03:59,364 --> 00:04:00,804
who has connections.

80
00:04:01,364 --> 00:04:02,004
You?

81
00:04:02,763 --> 00:04:03,364
Who has?

82
00:04:03,564 --> 00:04:04,323
Do you have any?

83
00:04:05,883 --> 00:04:07,084
Not to mention higher-ups,

84
00:04:07,084 --> 00:04:10,643
