higher than my father's?

85
00:04:11,284 --> 00:04:13,323
Mr. He,

86
00:04:13,763 --> 00:04:15,763
just calm down.

87
00:04:16,364 --> 00:04:19,284
In Deep In The Bustle,

88
00:04:19,643 --> 00:04:22,244
