89
00:04:23,963 --> 00:04:25,244
Cut the nonsense.

90
00:04:27,883 --> 00:04:28,443
Peter.

91
00:04:33,963 --> 00:04:34,763
Yunyan,

92
00:04:35,283 --> 00:04:36,364
let me tell you,

93
00:04:36,724 --> 00:04:40,124
either find me some girls
with high status,

94
00:04:40,283 --> 00:04:42,364
or promote me to the Tian Level.

95
00:04:43,364 --> 00:04:44,564
Do you hear me?

96
00:04:46,164 --> 00:04:49,244
Don't be in such a hurry.

97
00:04:49,283 --> 00:04:50,564
I'll go apply right now.

98
00:04:50,963 --> 00:04:52,283
I'm going now.

99
00:04:53,164 --> 00:04:54,083
Mr. He,

100
00:04:55,004 --> 00:04:57,443
look at that waitress over there.

101
00:04:58,364 --> 00:05:01,763
Her resources are unimaginably vast.

102
00:05:04,564 --> 00:05:05,763
You few, stay here.

103
00:05:05,763 --> 00:05:08,283
Keep Mr. He and the guests
happy with drinks.

104
00:05:08,684 --> 00:05:09,564
Go.

105
00:05:10,283 --> 00:05:11,763
The rest of you, come with me.

106
00:06:06,364 --> 00:06:07,564
Hello, Feng.

107
00:06:08,564 --> 00:06:10,203
Let me say this one more time.

108
00:06:10,523 --> 00:06:11,763
Call me

109
00:06:12,643 --> 00:06:13,564
"Boss".

110
00:06:18,364 --> 00:06:19,283
Yes, Boss.

111
00:06:19,323 --> 00:06:19,963
Go ahead.

112
00:06:21,443 --> 00:06:23,244
That's more like it.

113
00:06:24,083 --> 00:06:26,364
Unless Lu and the others are present,

114
00:06:27,283 --> 00:06:29,763
