115
00:06:32,083 --> 00:06:33,843
"Boss".

116
00:06:35,883 --> 00:06:36,924
Yes, Boss.

117
00:06:37,684 --> 00:06:39,684
Stay away from

118
00:06:40,124 --> 00:06:41,323
He Mike's project.

119
00:06:42,244 --> 00:06:44,044
I'll have someone take over from you.

120
00:06:44,523 --> 00:06:46,124
I've taken over the project.

121
00:06:46,124 --> 00:06:47,044
What comes next is...

122
00:06:47,044 --> 00:06:48,564
Do I need to repeat myself?

123
00:06:54,963 --> 00:06:56,124
No, Boss.

124
00:07:18,403 --> 00:07:21,484
What a pity for my string of beads.

125
00:07:23,044 --> 00:07:25,724
Tu Jiasheng...

126
00:07:28,192 --> 00:07:31,810
(Nie Feng,
Founder of Deep In The Bustle Nightclub)

127
00:07:33,604 --> 00:07:34,724
Book the tickets.

128
00:07:35,724 --> 00:07:37,564
It's time to return home.

129
00:07:58,763 --> 00:07:59,364
Come on,

130
00:08:00,164 --> 00:08:01,484
sit here and drink with me.

131
00:08:02,124 --> 00:08:02,924
This is for you.

132
00:08:07,124 --> 00:08:08,244
No need, sir.

133
00:08:08,364 --> 00:08:09,484
I don't drink.

134
00:08:09,763 --> 00:08:11,763
I'll focus on providing you
with the best service.

135
00:08:14,643 --> 00:08:16,083
Interesting.

136
00:08:16,523 --> 00:08:17,883
Mr. He,

137
00:08:17,883 --> 00:08:18,963
her name is Su Yunian.

138
00:08:18,963 --> 00:08:20,924
She's new, a top student.

139
00:08:21,044 --> 00:08:22,164
Most importantly,

140
00:08:22,164 --> 00:08:23,883
she's a newbie,

141
00:08:24,244 --> 00:08:25,684
but a little quick-tempered.

142
00:08:28,083 --> 00:08:30,083
A newbie with quick temper.

143
00:08:30,763 --> 00:08:31,523
Not bad.

144
00:08:32,843 --> 00:08:34,604
I like that.

145
00:08:35,004 --> 00:08:35,643
Come on,

146
00:08:37,044 --> 00:08:38,923
sit here and drink with me.

147
00:08:39,084 --> 00:08:40,643
Don't push your luck.

148
00:08:40,643 --> 00:08:41,724
I have plenty of money.

149
00:08:42,844 --> 00:08:44,283
I'm sorry, Mr. He.

150
00:08:44,563 --> 00:08:46,084
As a VIP room attendant,

151
00:08:46,124 --> 00:08:47,683
I'll provide the service I should.

152
00:08:47,683 --> 00:08:49,163
You're pushing it.

153
00:08:49,803 --> 00:08:50,964
Mr. He,

154
00:08:50,964 --> 00:08:51,923
she's just a waitress.

155
00:08:51,923 --> 00:08:53,444
Please don't stoop to her level.

156
00:08:53,444 --> 00:08:55,444
Let's play a new game, Mr. He.

157
00:08:55,444 --> 00:08:56,364
Mr. He.

158
00:09:01,643 --> 00:09:02,444
Okay.

159
00:09:03,364 --> 00:09:04,124
Let's

160
00:09:04,763 --> 00:09:06,043
play a new game.

161
00:09:15,444 --> 00:09:17,084
Lu, are you busy?

162
00:09:17,084 --> 00:09:17,683
No.

163
00:09:17,844 --> 00:09:18,683
What's up, Jiasheng?

164
00:09:18,763 --> 00:09:20,364
Come with me for a patrol downstairs.

165
00:09:20,444 --> 00:09:22,523
You sound like something's wrong.

166
00:09:22,883 --> 00:09:23,563
See you there.

167
00:09:26,643 --> 00:09:27,324
Ms. Bai.

168
00:09:27,324 --> 00:09:28,244
Ms. Bai,

169
00:09:28,643 --> 00:09:29,244
today

170
00:09:29,244 --> 00:09:30,244
