171
00:09:30,244 --> 00:09:31,283
Two rooms are occupied.

172
00:09:31,523 --> 00:09:32,763
Mr. Peter from Haiwei,

173
00:09:32,964 --> 00:09:35,084
and Allens from Swire Group.

174
00:09:35,883 --> 00:09:36,444
Oh, right,

175
00:09:36,444 --> 00:09:37,923
a Victoria's Secret show starts

176
00:09:37,923 --> 00:09:38,724
after midnight.

177
00:09:38,724 --> 00:09:39,244
Okay.

178
00:09:39,523 --> 00:09:40,484
Ms. Bai,

179
00:09:40,484 --> 00:09:41,484
Ruoxi is gone ages ago.

180
00:09:41,484 --> 00:09:42,324
I'd like to go see...

181
00:09:42,324 --> 00:09:43,244
Get out!

182
00:09:45,763 --> 00:09:47,763
Su Yunian, what's wrong with you?

183
00:09:47,763 --> 00:09:48,964
No, Yunyan.

184
00:09:49,204 --> 00:09:50,004
Inside just now...

185
00:09:50,004 --> 00:09:51,724
How many days have you
even been working?

186
00:09:51,844 --> 00:09:54,016
On your very first day,
you argued with a guest,

187
00:09:54,016 --> 00:09:55,283
and now you get kicked out?

188
00:09:55,283 --> 00:09:56,324
Do you even want this job?

189
00:09:56,444 --> 00:09:57,563
Listen to me.

190
00:09:58,004 --> 00:09:59,043
Inside just now, they...

191
00:09:59,283 --> 00:10:00,364
They what?

192
00:10:00,364 --> 00:10:01,763
The customer is God!

193
00:10:01,763 --> 00:10:02,724
Got it?

194
00:10:05,964 --> 00:10:07,084
So what if they're God?

195
00:10:07,683 --> 00:10:09,043
They're human.

196
00:10:09,364 --> 00:10:10,563
Shouldn't act like beasts.

197
00:10:10,724 --> 00:10:11,283
You

198
00:10:11,324 --> 00:10:12,283
- Yunyan.
- are talking back?

199
00:10:14,523 --> 00:10:15,844
Who's in the Earl room today?

200
00:10:17,364 --> 00:10:18,283
So brazen?

201
00:10:18,923 --> 00:10:21,084
It's Peter from Haiwei

202
00:10:21,523 --> 00:10:22,763
and Mr. He.

203
00:10:23,563 --> 00:10:25,124
You don't know.

204
00:10:25,124 --> 00:10:26,364
Since his father

205
00:10:26,484 --> 00:10:27,923
