207
00:10:30,643 --> 00:10:32,163
But what can we do?

208
00:10:32,163 --> 00:10:34,484
He has a powerful father backing him.

209
00:10:36,763 --> 00:10:39,563
I heard he went to ring the bell
at NASDAQ this time.

210
00:10:39,763 --> 00:10:41,844
And even came back with a private jet.

211
00:10:41,923 --> 00:10:43,523
So you see,

212
00:10:43,883 --> 00:10:45,683
for such a big spender,

213
00:10:45,724 --> 00:10:47,563
we have to serve him well.

214
00:10:47,683 --> 00:10:48,763
Right?

215
00:10:51,364 --> 00:10:52,244
Tell me

216
00:10:52,763 --> 00:10:53,964
