217
00:10:54,204 --> 00:10:56,604
This is our GM, Ms. Bai.

218
00:10:56,844 --> 00:10:58,283
She's asking you a question.

219
00:10:59,964 --> 00:11:01,043
Hello, Ms. Bai.

220
00:11:02,324 --> 00:11:03,844
(According to Ruoxi's diary,)

221
00:11:04,324 --> 00:11:06,364
(this must be Bai Manni,)

222
00:11:06,364 --> 00:11:09,523
(the GM at Deep In The Bustle,
her counterpart.)

223
00:11:09,763 --> 00:11:11,043
She's asking you a question.

224
00:11:11,763 --> 00:11:12,563
Ms. Bai,

225
00:11:13,324 --> 00:11:14,163
inside just now,

226
00:11:14,163 --> 00:11:15,364
Mr. He forced me

227
00:11:15,883 --> 00:11:17,643
to stuff ice balls in there.

228
00:11:18,283 --> 00:11:19,923
I'm here to be a waitress,

229
00:11:20,244 --> 00:11:21,043
not to be

230
00:11:21,043 --> 00:11:22,563
their crazy outlet toy.

231
00:11:22,844 --> 00:11:23,883
Go fix your hair.

232
00:11:24,032 --> 00:11:24,964
I'll go check.

233
00:11:29,344 --> 00:11:34,444
(Earl)

234
00:11:34,444 --> 00:11:35,163
Enough?

235
00:11:35,163 --> 00:11:36,324
Enough? Enough?

236
00:11:36,324 --> 00:11:38,643
Are all the girls here so feisty?

237
00:11:38,643 --> 00:11:39,964
Calm down, Mr. He.

238
00:11:39,964 --> 00:11:40,883
Ms. Bai,

239
00:11:41,523 --> 00:11:42,763
