243
00:11:52,964 --> 00:11:54,244
Fine, skip it.

244
00:11:55,163 --> 00:11:57,364
Just upgrade me
to the top-floor VIP room.

245
00:11:57,364 --> 00:11:59,844
My dad and Mr. Tu are deep partners.

246
00:12:00,163 --> 00:12:01,844
