247
00:12:01,844 --> 00:12:02,923
Mr. He,

248
00:12:03,683 --> 00:12:05,964
let's discuss it later.

249
00:12:06,683 --> 00:12:07,484
As you know,

250
00:12:08,204 --> 00:12:09,844
girls at Deep In The Bustle

251
00:12:09,923 --> 00:12:11,204
are exceptionally talented

252
00:12:11,204 --> 00:12:12,124
and beautiful.

253
00:12:12,124 --> 00:12:13,568
What's that got to do

254
00:12:13,568 --> 00:12:14,484
with me?

255
00:12:15,923 --> 00:12:17,563
I think her chest is too small

256
00:12:17,563 --> 00:12:19,004
with bad visual appeal.

257
00:12:20,364 --> 00:12:22,084
Why wouldn't I put it here?

258
00:12:22,484 --> 00:12:23,523
Why?

259
00:12:27,403 --> 00:12:28,403
Besides,

260
00:12:29,204 --> 00:12:30,883
I prefer things ice-cold.

261
00:12:31,604 --> 00:12:32,803
Like this whiskey,

262
00:12:33,523 --> 00:12:35,803
no matter how fine
your winery's vintage,

263
00:12:36,084 --> 00:12:38,084
no matter how rare the year,

264
00:12:38,883 --> 00:12:40,124
if it's not chilled,

265
00:12:40,283 --> 00:12:43,364
