266
00:12:46,923 --> 00:12:47,763
Okay.

267
00:12:49,004 --> 00:12:50,923
Ms. Bai,

268
00:12:51,403 --> 00:12:53,163
no wonder you're the GM.

269
00:12:53,604 --> 00:12:54,563
Actually,

270
00:12:54,883 --> 00:12:56,403
