273
00:13:01,964 --> 00:13:03,283
I'd be deeply honored.

274
00:13:03,283 --> 00:13:05,484
She's our GM. I'll drink with you.

275
00:13:05,484 --> 00:13:06,324
Get lost!

276
00:13:06,444 --> 00:13:07,523
What's it to you?

277
00:13:16,364 --> 00:13:17,283
Having me accompany you

278
00:13:17,403 --> 00:13:18,444
