279
00:13:23,283 --> 00:13:24,084
Come on,

280
00:13:25,283 --> 00:13:26,844
don't talk about money.

281
00:13:26,844 --> 00:13:28,563
I've got plenty of money.

282
00:13:28,844 --> 00:13:29,844
Money's no object for me.

283
00:13:31,523 --> 00:13:32,324
Ms. Bai,

284
00:13:34,283 --> 00:13:35,084
please.

285
00:13:41,283 --> 00:13:42,084
Let go!

286
00:13:47,763 --> 00:13:49,883
