290
00:14:08,043 --> 00:14:09,403
Ten ice balls, one million.

291
00:14:09,472 --> 00:14:10,964
It's premium ice, so add 50,000 each.

292
00:14:10,964 --> 00:14:12,163
A total of 1.5 million.

293
00:14:18,444 --> 00:14:19,444
Here's the money.

294
00:14:20,923 --> 00:14:21,964
All on the card.

295
00:14:24,964 --> 00:14:26,283
A small penalty for a big lesson.

296
00:14:27,364 --> 00:14:29,683
Not exactly bone-chilling, is it?

297
00:14:33,084 --> 00:14:33,964
Remember this.

298
00:14:35,084 --> 00:14:36,563
The top floor of Deep In The Bustle

299
00:14:37,444 --> 00:14:38,883
isn't somewhere for anyone.

300
00:14:42,964 --> 00:14:44,643
Today, yours are bigger than mine.

301
00:14:48,683 --> 00:14:50,923
Bai Manni!

302
00:14:57,620 --> 00:15:01,294
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

303
00:15:01,593 --> 00:15:04,784
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

304
00:15:06,616 --> 00:15:10,237
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

305
00:15:10,786 --> 00:15:13,585
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

306
00:15:15,056 --> 00:15:18,912
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

307
00:15:19,010 --> 00:15:22,688
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

308
00:15:23,906 --> 00:15:27,904
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

309
00:15:28,231 --> 00:15:33,472
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

310
00:15:34,050 --> 00:15:38,184
♪I feel guilty♪

311
00:15:38,754 --> 00:15:42,592
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

312
00:15:43,362 --> 00:15:46,805
♪Even in tears♪

313
00:15:47,554 --> 00:15:51,584
♪It doesn't matter♪

314
00:15:51,650 --> 00:15:55,473
♪We embrace in dreams♪

315
00:15:56,322 --> 00:15:59,760
♪I let down all my defenses♪

316
00:16:00,994 --> 00:16:04,448
♪Though the story has its end♪

317
00:16:04,832 --> 00:16:14,208
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
